umzug.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please update my address in your records accordingly.

My new address:
{neueAdresse}

Effective from: {datum}

Please send all future correspondence to the new address and confirm that the change has been made.

nachsende.body:
I am writing to inform you that my post should be delivered to the following address:

{neueAdresse}

Effective from: {datum}

Please update your delivery records accordingly and confirm receipt of this request. If a separate form, identification or fee is required to set up a mail redirection, please let me know what you need from me.

maengel.body:
I am writing to report the following defect at the property {objekt}:

{mangel}

Requested date for the repair to be completed: {datum}

I ask you to arrange for the defect to be put right by that date. Please contact me to agree a suitable appointment for access if this is needed. If the defect is not remedied, I reserve the right to take such further steps as are available to me under my tenancy agreement and the law that applies where the property is located.

Please confirm receipt of this notice in writing.

kaution.body:
I am writing regarding the tenancy for the property at {objekt}, which has now ended. The property was handed back in accordance with the agreement.

End of tenancy: {datum}

I ask you to return the deposit in full, together with any interest due, to the following account:

Account holder: {name}
IBAN / account number: {iban}

If you intend to make any deduction from the deposit, please provide an itemised statement setting out the amount and the reason for each deduction, together with supporting evidence. Please also confirm receipt of this letter.

handy-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel my mobile phone contract, in accordance with the notice period stated in my contract.

Contract / customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the contract and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact end date in writing, and confirm that no further payments will be collected after that date. If my number is eligible to be transferred to another provider, please also send me the details I need for the transfer.

internet-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel my internet or broadband contract, in accordance with the notice period stated in my contract.

Contract / customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the contract and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact end date in writing, and confirm that no further payments will be collected after that date. Please also let me know how and by when any equipment belonging to you should be returned.

streaming-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel my streaming subscription, in accordance with the notice period stated in my contract.

Contract / customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the contract and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact end date in writing, and confirm that no further payments will be collected from my account after that date.

fitness-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel my gym membership, in accordance with the notice period stated in my membership agreement.

Membership / customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the agreement and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact end date in writing, confirm that the membership will not renew automatically, and confirm that no further payments will be collected after that date.

versicherung-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel the insurance policy referred to above, in accordance with the notice period stated in my policy documents.

Policy number: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the policy and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact date on which cover ends in writing, confirm that no further premiums will be collected after that date, and let me know whether any premium already paid will be refunded.

mitgliedschaft-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to end my membership, in accordance with the notice period set out in the membership terms or the organisation's rules.

Membership number: {vertragsnr}
Requested end date: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted and let me know that date.

Please confirm the end of my membership in writing, and confirm that no further contributions or fees will be collected after that date.

adress-behoerde.body:
I am writing to notify you of my new address. Please update my records accordingly.

My new address:
{neueAdresse}

Effective from: {datum}

Please send all future correspondence to this address and confirm the change in writing. If you require a separate form, proof of address or identification in order to process this change, please let me know what is needed.

namensaenderung.body:
I am writing to inform you that my name has changed.

Previous name: {altName}
New name: {neuName}
Effective from: {datum}

Please update your records accordingly and confirm the change in writing. If you require documentary evidence of the change of name, please let me know which document you need and I will provide a copy.

kindergeld.body:
I am writing in connection with my entitlement to child benefit or family-related payments to notify you of the following:

{text}

Reference number: {vertragsnr}

Please take this information into account when assessing my entitlement and update your records accordingly. If any further information or supporting evidence is required, please let me know what you need and by when.

Please confirm receipt of this notification.

steuer-adress.body:
I am writing to notify you of my new address for tax purposes. Please update my records accordingly.

My new address:
{neueAdresse}

Tax reference number: {vertragsnr}
Effective from: {datum}

Please send all future correspondence, assessments and notices to this address and confirm the change in writing. If this change needs to be submitted through a particular form or online service, please let me know.

arbeit-bank.body:
I am writing to let you know that my bank details for salary payments have changed. Please pay my salary into the following account:

Account holder: {name}
IBAN / account number: {iban}

Effective from: {datum}

Please confirm the change in writing before the next payroll run. If you require this instruction on a particular form or through the employee self-service system, please let me know.

elternzeit.body:
I am writing to request parental leave for the period set out below.

Start of leave: {von}
End of leave: {bis}

I am happy to discuss the details with you, including how my duties can best be covered during my absence and any part-time or phased return arrangements.

Please confirm the leave in writing, together with any conditions, notice requirements or supporting documents that apply under my contract and under the rules in force where I am employed.

urlaub.body:
I am writing to request annual leave for the period set out below.

From: {von}
To: {bis}

I will make sure my current work is handed over before I go. Please let me know if a different period would fit better with the team's planning.

Please confirm the leave. Thank you.

fin-bank.body:
I am writing to notify you of my new bank details. Please collect any amounts due from the following account:

Account holder: {name}
IBAN / account number: {iban}
Customer reference: {vertragsnr}

Effective from: {datum}

Please confirm the change in writing and confirm that no further amounts will be taken from my previous account. If a new direct debit mandate or authorisation form is required, please send it to me.

lastschrift.body:
I am writing to cancel the direct debit mandate or recurring payment authorisation you hold for my account.

Customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Amount concerned: {betrag}
Date from which the cancellation applies: {datum}

Please do not collect any further payments from my account from that date and confirm the cancellation in writing.

If any amount is still genuinely due under our contract, please send me an invoice setting out what is owed and why, and I will arrange payment separately. Please note that cancelling this authorisation does not by itself terminate the underlying contract.

reklamation.body:
A payment has been taken from my account which I do not agree with, and I am writing to dispute it.

Amount: {betrag}
Date of the payment: {datum}

The reason for my objection is as follows:

{text}

I ask you to review the transaction and to refund the amount to my account. Please also confirm what, if anything, you need from me in order to complete the review, and let me know how long it will take.

Please confirm receipt of this complaint. If you are unable to resolve it, please let me know how I can escalate it and which complaints body or ombudsman scheme covers your service.

ratenzahlung.body:
I am writing about the outstanding balance on my account to ask whether it would be possible to pay in instalments.

Invoice / customer reference: {vertragsnr}
Outstanding amount: {betrag}

{text}

My current financial circumstances mean that I am not able to settle the full amount in a single payment, but I do want to clear the balance and I am able to make regular payments towards it.

I would be grateful if you would agree to an instalment arrangement and confirm it in writing, including the amount and due date of each instalment. Please also confirm that no further charges, interest or recovery action will be added while the agreed instalments are being paid on time.

strom.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please transfer my electricity contract to my new address:

{neueAdresse}

Meter / customer number: {vertragsnr}
Date of the move: {datum}

Please let me know which meter readings and documents you need from me, whether the supply at the new address can be taken over on the same contract, and whether any change to my tariff will apply. Please confirm the transfer in writing and send me a final statement for the old address.

gas.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please transfer my gas contract to my new address:

{neueAdresse}

Meter / customer number: {vertragsnr}
Date of the move: {datum}

Please let me know which meter readings and documents you need from me, whether the supply at the new address can be taken over on the same contract, and whether any change to my tariff will apply. Please confirm the transfer in writing and send me a final statement for the old address.

wasser.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please transfer my water account to my new address:

{neueAdresse}

Meter / customer number: {vertragsnr}
Date of the move: {datum}

Please let me know which meter readings and documents you need from me, and whether the account at the new address needs to be opened separately. Please confirm the change in writing and send me a final statement for the old address.

muell.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please update the account for waste collection and refuse charges to my new address:

{neueAdresse}

Account / file reference: {vertragsnr}
Date of the move: {datum}

Please let me know what you need from me in order to close the account for my old address and to register the new one, including any arrangements for collecting or delivering bins or containers. Please confirm the change in writing and send me a final statement for the old address.

rundfunk.body:
I am writing to let you know that I am moving. Please update my address for the public broadcasting fee or licence:

{neueAdresse}

Account / licence number: {vertragsnr}
Date of the move: {datum}

Please confirm the change in writing and let me know whether any payment is due or refundable as a result, and whether any separate form or declaration is required for the new address.

kfz-vers-kuend.body:
I am writing to give notice to cancel the motor insurance policy for my vehicle, in accordance with the notice period stated in my policy documents.

Vehicle registration number: {kennzeichen}
Policy number: {vertragsnr}
Requested end of cover: {datum}

If cancellation to that date is not possible, please treat this as notice for the earliest date permitted under the policy and let me know that date.

Please confirm the cancellation and the exact date on which cover ends in writing, confirm that no further premiums will be collected, and let me know whether any premium already paid will be refunded. Please also send me a statement of my claims and no-claims history for use with a new insurer.

I am aware that motor insurance is compulsory in most countries and I will ensure that replacement cover is in place before this policy ends.

fahrzeug-anab.body:
I am writing regarding the registration of my vehicle.

Vehicle registration number: {kennzeichen}

{text}

Requested effective date: {datum}

Please let me know which documents, forms and evidence you require from me, whether the matter can be dealt with by post or online, and whether any fee is payable. Please also confirm what will happen to the registration documents and number plates.

Please confirm receipt of this request and let me know once it has been processed.

halterwechsel.body:
I am writing to notify you of a change of registered keeper for my vehicle.

Vehicle registration number: {kennzeichen}

Details of the new keeper:

{text}

Requested effective date: {datum}

Please let me know which documents and forms are required to complete the transfer, whether both parties need to sign, and whether any fee is payable. Please also confirm from which date I am no longer responsible for the vehicle, including for any tax, charges or penalties.

Please confirm receipt of this notification and send me written confirmation once the change has been recorded.

adress-freunde.body:
We would like to let you know that we have moved. Our new address is:

{neueAdresse}

We can be reached there from: {datum}

Our phone numbers and email addresses stay the same. We would love to see you at our new place, so do get in touch — you are very welcome to visit.

namens-mitteilen.body:
I would like to let you know that my name has changed.

Previous name: {altName}
New name: {neuName}
Effective from: {datum}

Nothing else changes — same person, same phone number, same email address. I would be grateful if you could use my new name from now on and update it in your contacts. Thank you.

todesfall.body:
It is with great sadness that we must let you know that {verstorben} has died.

Date of death: {sterbedatum}

{text}

We are grateful for the kindness and friendship shown over the years, and we know that this news will be difficult for many of you to receive.

Details of the funeral arrangements will follow. In the meantime we ask for your quiet thoughts and for your understanding if we are slow to reply to messages.

vollmacht.body:
I, {name}, hereby authorise the following person to act on my behalf:

{bevoll}

The authorisation covers the following matter:

{zweck}

Effective from: {datum}

This authorisation remains in force until I revoke it in writing. The authorised person may take the steps and make the statements reasonably required to deal with the matter described above on my behalf. It does not extend to any other matter.

Please note: the formal requirements for an authorisation of this kind vary from country to country, and for property, banking, health and legal proceedings a notarised or otherwise formally executed document is often required. Please confirm whether this document is sufficient for your purposes or whether a specific form is needed.
